@startuml sequence_position
title SideHustle Position Creation Sequence

actor User
participant Client
participant "Server\n(Position API + services)" as Server
database Database
participant "ConnectHub Classifieds" as ConnectHub

User -> Client: 1 Click create new position button on SideHustle page
Client --> User: 2 Display position creation form
User -> Client: 3 Fill out position title, description, and submit
Client -> Server: 4 Send position creation request with SideHustle ID and details
Server -> Database: 5 Validate SideHustle ownership
Database --> Server: 6 Ownership confirmed
Server -> Database: 7 Insert new position with OPEN status\nupdate side_hustles.has_open_positions = true
Database --> Server: 8 Position creation success response
Server --> Client: 9 Return created position payload (new position ID)
Client --> User: 10 Display position creation success message

ConnectHub -> Server: 11 GET /launchpad/positions/{positionId}/status (public)
Server -> Database: 12 Read positions.status
Database --> Server: 13 OPEN | FILLED | CLOSED
Server --> ConnectHub: 14 Return plain status string

@enduml